        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer198277857" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4268883443944607298">This is a wonderfully written Retelling of Little Red Riding Hood filled with love and Romance as well as a touch of mystery and some unexpected twists and surprises that will keep you entertained and interested throughout the story. All the characters are very well written as well as all the different relationships that are present throughout the story. I particularly enjoyed reading about the relationship between Ruth and William and seeing how it developed.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


