<div id="review_105591602" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/105591602" />
    <a title="Tammie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3506989-tammie"><img alt="Tammie" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1604938056p2/3506989.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/105591602?book_show_action=true">Jun 04, 2010</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Tammie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Tammie" href="/user/show/3506989-tammie">Tammie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3506989-tammie?shelf=retellings">retellings</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3506989-tammie?shelf=owned-mass-market-paper-back">owned-mass-market-paper-back</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3506989-tammie?shelf=adult">adult</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3506989-tammie?shelf=urban-fantasy">urban-fantasy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3506989-tammie?shelf=fantasy">fantasy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3506989-tammie?shelf=historical-fantasy">historical-fantasy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3506989-tammie?shelf=stand-alones">stand-alones</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3506989-tammie?shelf=adult-fantasy">adult-fantasy</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer105591602" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17899554284631822319">I really liked this retelling of Red Riding Hood. There were no big surprises in it, but I loved the story anyway. There was plenty of romance and passion but it was still a clean love story which was nice. Some of the dialog between the two main characters got a bit cheesy during the romance scenes, but I was able to ignore it. Overall I thought it was a fun, quick read.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


